Early Access Review

0.74.something
Started out as a man with the sword of the gods;
.....
5 min in: gets beaten up by starving thugs with iron sticks (there were 6 of them!!!!);

10 min: limped back to city and payed outrageous bed rental for healing purposes(ONLY);

12 min: goes to bar and made a friend by paying them(thats how you get friends in life if you have no choice);

15 min: finished customizing friend;

20 min: ninjas fight the town guards;

22 min: rob ninjas for thier clothes and weapons;

23 min: sold whatever not needed;

24 min: ventures out for hours and builds a city and made a mercenary group named Band of the Hawk;

27 min: get attacked by giraffe thingy??? barely survives....again;

Hours upon hours in : Strong thriving, never seen much wildlife;

*updates to latest update*

started as a group of 5 robot nobodies;

5 min: gets torn apart by giant giraffe bird things;

restarted with another group: torn up by Giraffe birds known as beak things (lone survivor watched in horror as his comrades were left dying near the beak things sleeping on top of them;

third group: survived and spent hours building a house with crossbows on top;

hours: no more beak things HUNT THEM ALLL (just not on foot they are deadly);

10/10 would get devoured (BROKEN!!!) by beak things in a harsh land again
In all serioness this is a game that will stomp you down if you dont play it smart, but it is redicously fun and i can recommend it and the dev are working hard, trust me i follow their blogs. AND REMEMBER its an ALPHA its not perfect it can stress you out with the ocassional bugs and graphics card death threats (never really happens at all its just me i swear) but its great in my opinion, Keep up the good work Lo-Fi, keep it up.
